'''Orbital Defense Command''' was the branch of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] that was placed in charge of defending [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] spaceways. It was based in [[Orbital Defense Headquarters]]; as of [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]], it had been placed under the command of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Ba'tra]].

